response.overview: When they take some friends on an extreme sport adventure, the last thing Jared and Sam expect to see below the shark-infested waters is a legendary pirate ship rumored to contain millions of dollars in gold. But their good fortune is short-lived, as a ruthless gang of criminals gets word of what they have uncovered.
response.title: Into the Blue

release_dates.note: Rio de Janeiro International Film Festival

results.name: Jared Discovers A Mysterious Underwater Artifact
Would You Give Up Treasure for Love?
